{"type": "article", "id": 12447, "title": "金字塔状吊灯", "description": "", "date": "2015-07-22T07:45:26Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 12, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000224pGle5jfIrbiyxaB6.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是一套 3D 打印而来的吊灯，上部使用的是榉木材料，而下部的框架部分由 3D 打印而成。吊灯“灯罩”使用金字塔的形状，而设计师也坦言灵感的确来自金字塔，既能够有效保护光源，又能增加吊灯的庄严感和仪式感。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261402071eFAJ4QzrsXNjUfw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/2016072614020847clrC1BPFX5mRJH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140209dz4JPsrgfN7y8eD9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140209G1P2ZuNEQJKt4dV5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140210v9LXZ0ftmcGd4uw6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}